There was a question.

00:42:02.830 --> 00:42:04.320
AUDIENCE: Oh yes.

00:42:04.320 --> 00:42:08.730
Not related to this, but what
household characteristics does

00:42:08.730 --> 00:42:15.463
[INAUDIBLE] economic ones like
