00:43:08.750 --> 00:43:12.430
but maybe be a little leery
that at least in the case

00:43:12.430 --> 00:43:16.190
of Thailand, you think about
starting at a low level--

00:43:16.190 --> 00:43:18.230
and some of these guys
remain in poverty,

00:43:18.230 --> 00:43:22.090
but there is a huge
growth dynamic going on.

00:43:22.090 --> 00:43:22.700
Yes?

